Package com.milk.uberchat.icb

Interface Summary
ICBListener This is the interface for objects that care about ICBEvents.
 

Class Summary
ICBChannel This is the ChatChannel class for ICB channels.
ICBEvent This class is for representing some of the special packets that an ICB server sends to the client.
ICBIdentity This is the ChatIdentity class for an ICB identity.
ICBInputFilter This class is a filter on incoming data from an ICB connection.
ICBInteractor This class does all the interaction with an ICB server.
ICBSystem This is the ICB-specific ChatSystem.
ICBSystemTemplate This is the template class for ICBSystems.
ICBUser This is the ChatUser class for an ICB user.
ICBWho This class merely holds data representing a "who" line.
